      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/002/755/160/original/4c55c974-a334-47f1-b333-6c96afd11604.png" srcset="" alt="Open Settings" height="275" width="158">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_B6B3D740-22D4-0135-E076-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p><span style="color:rgb(49,49,49);">In Course Navigation, click the <strong>Settings</strong> link.</span></p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

