      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="view_links" data-step-uuid="2bb3a657-f46f-46d7-b249-fe2e93b419d3">
    <h2 id="view_links" class="step-title screensteps-heading">View Links</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/002/598/906/original/593da42f-18fa-499c-af3a-93585a4af0ca.png" srcset="" alt="View Links" height="381" width="678">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_B6B52520-22D4-0135-E07C-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>If any links are found in the course, Canvas displays the number of links [1], followed by the name of the content item and the content's associated invalid link(s) [2].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="view_unpublished_content" data-step-uuid="b120feed-bb3c-45b6-a43a-a86462ed89ba">
