  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_B6B55C90-22D4-0135-E07E-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>The validator displays broken links and images by item type [1]. Â Broken content is identified as either a link or an image [2]. Non-existent content means that the object is invalid and should be replaced [3]. Unreachable objects mean the image could not be displayed [4].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
