      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_B6B631B0-22D4-0135-E082-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>To update links within course content, click the name of the content item [1].</p>
<p>After you update your content, you can validate your links again by returning to the Link Validator page and clicking the <strong>Restart Link Validation </strong>button [2]. </p>
  </div>
